  "texts": [
    "RAVEN is equipped with two external offline tools: a calculator and a SQL engine.",
    "The Calculator is instantiated in a python interpreter and is used to evaluate well-formed arithmetic expressions.",
    "The API expects one input representing the arithmetic expression and returns the evaluated result.",
    "The Lightweight SQL engine is an API capable of executing SQL scripts on relational data.",
    "The API expects two inputs, (1) a string representation of the structured data and (2) a SQL script."
  ],
